# Configuration is split across two components:
#
#   addon/   — ServiceM8 SimpleFunction (settings configured in SM8 Developer Console)
#   worker/  — Cloudflare Worker (secrets set via Wrangler)
#
# See README.md for full setup instructions.
#
# Cloudflare Worker secrets (set with: wrangler secret put SM8_ACCESS_TOKEN):
#   SM8_ACCESS_TOKEN=<your ServiceM8 OAuth access token>
#
# Cloudflare Worker vars (set in worker/wrangler.toml [vars]):
#   SM8_PARTS_TO_ORDER_QUEUE_UUID=
#   SM8_READY_TO_BOOK_QUEUE_UUID=
